### 10. Director Attendance: Working Days Setting Dibaca Salah
**File:** [direkturRoutes.js](file:///c:/ADAM/smart_attendance_system/backend/src/routes/direkturRoutes.js#L170-L171)

```javascript
// ❌ Menggunakan findFirst (semua settings), bukan mencari key tertentu
const settings = await prisma.settings.findFirst();
const workingDays = settings?.workingDays ? settings.workingDays.split(',').map(...) : [...];
```

`Settings` model menggunakan key-value pair, bukan field langsung. Seharusnya:
```javascript
const s = await prisma.settings.findUnique({ where: { key: 'workingDays' } });
const workingDays = s ? JSON.parse(s.value) : [1,2,3,4,5];
```

